If you feel like adding a dash of old Hollywood style to your wardrobe you could channel your inner Cary Grant and bag Breitling’s Premier B01 Chronograph 42. It’s an example of understated elegance and takes its inspiration from the brand’s premier watches, manufactured in the 1940s. This modern iteration sports astainless steel 42mm case with a transparent caseback, and is available with a dark blue or silver dial. There are leather, nubuk and stainless steel straps. Price? Around ? in the region of R124,000. Breitling.com